Params: {2: 'Karenina', 3: "...I've changed a lot, too. I won't just keep my mouth shut now.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'What are you trying to say?', 3: '11', 4: "Weren't you like that before?", 5: '12'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "I'll get stronger... stronger than everyone. I'll be able to help you more than anyone.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'You can play tricks on other Constructs, but not me...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'I knew that mission was dangerous, but I want to prove myself to you.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Sorry, I got carried away. I need to go for a walk, Commandant...', 4: '1'}
